00:41:21,360 --> 00:41:23,250
from paying for what you did.

551
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:25,840
Ru-na.

552
00:41:26,640 --> 00:41:28,620
Have you ever

553
00:41:29,800 --> 00:41:32,710
loved someone with all of your heart?

554
00:41:34,200 --> 00:41:35,300
Are you that stupid?

555
00:41:36,620 --> 00:41:38,120
Whom do you think I did all of this for?

556
00:41:38,210 --> 00:41:39,660
Stop lying.

557
00:41:40,360 --> 00:41:42,340
You've never loved Ni-na.

558
00:41:42,610 --> 00:41:45,030
You would never do this
if you truly loved her.

559
00:41:45,120 --> 00:41:47,580
You would rather die,
so you could save that person.

560
00:41:50,400 --> 00:41:52,290
You have never

561
00:41:53,700 --> 00:41:55,240
felt this way. Not once.

562
00:41:55,460 --> 00:41:57,260
That's why your heart is empty.

563
00:41:57,350 --> 00:41:59,770
And you're desperately trying to
fill that empty heart.

564
00:42:01,350 --> 00:42:03,200
What do you know?
How dare you run your mouth?

565
00:42:03,290 --> 00:42:04,430
I truly

566
00:42:04,960 --> 00:42:06,720
pity you

567
00:42:07,640 --> 00:42:09,270
because you will live here
for the rest of your life

568
00:42:09,360 --> 00:42:12,170
without knowing
how precious and beautiful love is.

569
00:42:15,030 --> 00:42:16,440
Stay healthy.

570
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:37,250
Why did you want to come here?

571
00:42:37,340 --> 00:42:39,410
I'm sure just the sight of her
disgusts you.

572
00:42:39,500 --> 00:42:41,080
I wanted to tell her

573
00:42:41,700 --> 00:42:43,680
that it was a total defeat of hers.

574
00:42:46,100 --> 00:42:47,680
You're back, Young Lady.

575
00:42:48,080 --> 00:42:49,130
I'm happy.

576
00:42:50,810 --> 00:42:52,520
Now that everything is settled,

577
00:42:52,790 --> 00:42:55,340
